), hairdryer and telephone. You can also enjoy all the Hotel Atolon offers you: 2 bars one inside and another one at the outside terrace where you will be able to taste their wide and varied menu which, with the wonderful views, will make you feel relaxed. All meals are served in the restaurant with a great buffet (Breakfast and dinner). At midday you will be able to enjoy the wide and varied menu in the snack/restaurant at the terrace. In the restaurant in front of the sea, you will be able to taste all the dishes at midday or enjoying an amazing dusk.
The hotel also offers free breakfast to its guests.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>SurroundingArea</Type><Text>Cala Bona was an old port, a refuge for the fishermen. Atolon hotel is located at the promenade of Cala Bona, near the fishing port where you will be able to taste the best fish of the area in any of its restaurants.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Due to the urban development, caused by the tourism boom, the appearance of the area has changed, linking Cala Bona with Cala Millor. Nowadays, theres a pedestrian street that goes from Cala Bona to Cala Millor. Cala Bona and Cala Millor have good quality and developed touristic facilities. You will find restaurants, discos, different kind of shops, markets&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;The beach of Cala Bona, at the bay of Cala Millor, has the blue flag, certification which is given by the NGO called ADEAC(Association of environmental and consumer education). Cala Millor is located at the east coast of Mallorca, a place where you can practise many sports or simply rest and relax near the sea.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>RoomTypes</Type><Text>DOUBLE - B_AND_B - The room offers 2 twin beds and 1 double bed. Double room with balcony, bathroom with bathtube. Air Conditioning / Heating, Telephone, Minibar, Hair dryer and safe. Breakfast included.

